    "We next clarify what guarantee M is necessary and sufficient for an LLM to generalize in a research context, and therefore whether it is a general-purpose technology for prediction.",
    "Under Assumption 1, for any research context Q(•)∈Q and text generator m(•),",
    "Proposition 1.",
    "The large language model m(•;t) generalizes for research context Q(•)∈Q if and only if it satisfies the guarantee M(Q) for",
    "Consequently, the LLM m(•;t) is a general-purpose technology for prediction if and only if it satisfies the guarantee Q∈Q M(Q)."
  ]
}